+Phase 12.6 — Character Card Compatibility Layer
+Goal
+
+Add a compatibility layer for importing/exporting external character cards without letting imported prompt structures become simulation truth.
+
+Imported cards must be treated as:
+
+seed data
+presentation/personality hints
+optional world/setup hints
+
+Never as authoritative simulation state by themselves.
